Optimizes fonts for better readability. &bull; Optimizes system icons by using the latest color scheme to make the icons easier to recognize. &bull; Enriches and optimizes illustrations for features by incorporating multicultural and inclusive elements.  【Efficiency】 &bull; Adds Meeting Assistant to enhance the meeting connecting and note-taking experience and introduces an option to make notifications more subtle and less distracting. &bull; Adds support for one-tap meeting joining and smart meeting minutes to improve work efficiency. &bull; Adds large folders to the Home screen. You can now open an app in an enlarged folder with just one tap and turn pages in the folder with a swipe. &bull; Adds a new type of Always-On Display that shows live information about music, ride-hailing, and food delivery. (Supports only some apps) &bull; Adds NFC university card. You can now use your phone as your university card. (This feature is only available in some universities.) &bull; Adds support to double tap the power button to show your health code. &bull; Adds media playback control, and optimizes the Quick Settings experience. &bull; Adds smart event management and conflict reminders to help with your scheduling. &bull; Adds support for one-tap calendar sync to DingTalk and one-tap sync of email events. &bull; Adds support for event recognition. You can use screen recognition to recognize and sync the events on the current screen to Calendar with one tap. &bull; Adds more markup tools for screenshot editing. &bull; Adds support for adding widgets to the Home screen, making information display more personalized. &bull; Adds support for conversion of images in Photos to .doc, .ppt, and .xlsx formats. &bull; Upgrades to Text scanner 2.0, which can recognize text and extract information from scanned images in multiple scenarios. &bull; Upgrades Doodle in Notes. You can now draw on graphics to take notes more efficiently. &bull; Upgrades Recorder. Search capabilities are enhanced and exporting images and text is supported. &bull; Optimizes Breeno Suggestions to make scenario-based suggestions for apps and services.  【Seamless interconnection】 &bull; Upgrades to Multi-Screen Connect 2.0. You can answer or hang up calls on a connected PC and even switch a call between your phone and PC. &bull; Optimizes Multi-Screen Connect. You can open multiple mobile apps on a connected PC for efficient multitasking. &bull; Optimizes cross-device file transfer, with more file formats and device models supported. &bull; Optimizes Screencast, with cast content automatically adapting to the target screen.  【Personalization】 &bull; Adds more Omoji materials to cover more scenarios. Omoji now supports to set the contacts avatars, fully expressing yourself with more customized avatars. &bull; Adds Insight Always-On Display, with more personalized Always-On Display settings available. &bull; Optimizes Portrait Silhouette Always-On Display, with more drawing tools and line colors available.  【Security &amp; privacy】 &bull; Adds an automatic pixelation feature for chat screenshots. The system can identify and automatically pixelate profile pictures and display names in a chat screenshot to protect your privacy. &bull; Adds smart permission suggestions to improve security. &bull; Adds a feature to prevent malicious attempts to lure users into installing apps, supporting smart blocking of malicious pop-ups and promotions. &bull; Adds regular clearing of clipboard data for privacy protection. &bull; Optimizes Private Safe. The Advanced Encryption Standard (AES) is used to encrypt all files for enhanced security of private files. &bull; Optimizes payment security.  【Health &amp; Digital wellbeing】 &bull; When in Kid Space, your browser app automatically switches to Kids mode to create a child-friendly space. &bull; Adds ambient light reminders in Kid Space. &bull; Adds Eye comfort in Kid Space to protect children's vision. &bull; Adds family health data in O Family. You can check the data to understand your family members' health status. &bull; Adds notifications when O Family detecting abnormal health data and human falling on the ground  【Performance optimization】 &bull; Adds Dynamic Computing Engine to improve the system speed, stability, battery life, and app experience. &bull; Upgrades to LinkBoost 4.0, which can detect and improve the network quality for faster download speeds, even in very slow network conditions. &bull; Optimizes the IEM ecosystem to include more apps.  【Gaming experience】 &bull; Adds self-developed VRS technology, which dynamically adjusts the resolution to increase the performance while saving power so as to improve the gaming experience. &bull; Upgrades to HyperBoost GPA 4.0 to stabilize the frame rate and balance the performance and power consumption in key scenarios.&quot; ","companyName":null,"fileSize":17612989178,"softwareVersion":null,"projectNo":"20031","host":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com","nvFileInfo":[]}]}]},{"osVersion":"ColorOS 14.0.0","packageInfo":[{"versionType":"normal","packageInfoDetail":[{"inSalesLink":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com/dfs/25/03/31/52a481599c334a1a8f2405f270215418.zip","outSalesLink":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com/dfs/25/03/31/52a481599c334a1a8f2405f270215418.zip","marketModel":"OPPO Find X3 Pro","updateDesc":null,"googlePatchDate":"2025/03/01 00:00:00","type":"normal","versionFilename":"PEEM00domestic_11_14.0.0.618CN01_2025022719460203.zip","backVersionLink":"https://gpw13.myoas.com/artifactory/after-sale-local/20series/20031_14.0_U/%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC/MP14/PEEM00domestic_11_14.0.0.618CN01_2025022719460203.zip","filePath":"/dfs/25/03/31/52a481599c334a1a8f2405f270215418.zip","fileName":"PEEM00domestic_11_14.0.0.618CN01_2025022719460203.zip","md5":"12d24914eb42afa00be8433d2615bd47","colorOs":"ColorOS 14.0.0","androidVersion":"Android 14","updateDescEnglish":null,"companyName":null,"fileSize":8083959541,"softwareVersion":"14.0